    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Itty Bitty Toilet Kitty Demo! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/ab821a993379ba6520f60a16f99ca435.poster.avif?t=1738582064\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/ab821a993379ba6520f60a16f99ca435.webm?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/ab821a993379ba6520f60a16f99ca435.mp4?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BE A CAT and SAVE YOUR HUMAN! In Itty Bitty Toilet Kitty you get to play as a cute feline who must protect their owner from the flesh eating toilet monsters - GREEBLES.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.poster.avif?t=1738582064\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.webm?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/7aa3bf4d36360d29c834bde402c81bce.mp4?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase, jump and slash them down, until there are none left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.poster.avif?t=1738582064\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.webm?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/ced29341db06dfd3b9d8a297790af76b.mp4?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Art and a Retro soundtrack, Itty-Bitty Toilet Kitty is a micro game with a big kitty bite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.poster.avif?t=1738582064\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.webm?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283850/extras/c0d58ca76570bfca95dc0b4c0eedf1b8.mp4?t=1738582064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full game is expected to be released in March!</p>",
